name: De Netyu
overview:
Established in the year 2011, we, “De Netyug”, are one of the renowned manufacturers and suppliers of Video Surveillance, Fire Alarm & Biometric Access Control Systems. Products offered are Night Vision Camera, Bullet Camera, Box Camera, Color Dome Camera, IP Analog Gateway, DVRs, CCTV Cameras and Addressable & Conventional Fire Alarm System.

Our Team: Engineers Skilled workers Technicians Quality auditors Warehousing experts Sales and marketing executives

Quality Assurance: Quality remains a strengthening factor, which enables us to gain a firm foothold in this stiff market competition. We have constructed an advanced quality testing laboratory, which is equipped with all the needed amenities essential for offering a defect-free range of Video Surveillance, Fire Alarm & Biometric Access Control Systems.

Client Satisfaction: We are able to attain maximum satisfaction of our esteemed clients by consistently offering an unparalleled range of Video Surveillance, Fire Alarm & Biometric Access Control Systems.

Why Us?: Today’s market is highly competitive yet we stand on top in the market owing to our quality oriented business operations. We have tie ups only with the reliable and authentic vendors of the market. They manufacture these products with ultra grade components implementing latest technologies.

Infrastructure: We have constructed a sophisticated infrastructure, which helps us in carrying out the business related activities in a streamlined manner. The facility is installed with modern machines and innovative technology that aid us in offering an extensive assembly of Video Surveillance, Fire Alarm & Biometric Access Control Systems.
